*        triplet.spt - Simple text formatting
*        Reformats a file by centering the lines and arranging them in groups of three.

         &TRIM    =  1
         N        =  0
LOOP     S        =  INPUT                                  :F(END)
         OUTPUT   =  DUPL(' ', (80 - SIZE(S)) / 2) S
         N        =  REMDR(N + 1, 3)
         OUTPUT   =  EQ(N, 0)                               :(LOOP)
END
